"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"# 1.  Gas estimate tool\\n\\na chrome extension show the current base fee of Ethereum\\n\\nwe know Concave is a cross chain yield agg for ohm forks, but ethereum is\\n\\nlikely to be the main land for us, so it‘s great tool for you to decide when it is best for you to send a transaction.\\n\\n![Base fee is updated every 5 seconds](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/PaL3ypuFffrTzZtjNkTLh.png?height=92&width=567)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/i7zhJ5cks_T--wohJygEc.png?height=966&width=1600)\\n\\nopen chrome(or chrome based browsers, eg brave), and install with below link.\\n\\n[https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/blocknative-eth-gas-estim/ablbagjepecncofimgjmdpnhnfjiecfm](https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/blocknative-eth-gas-estim/ablbagjepecncofimgjmdpnhnfjiecfm)\\n\\n# 2.  Zapper Dashboard\\n\\nWith zapper , you can track your DeFi portfolio in one place, as we know Concave may support multiple chains like Matic BSC…you may need it to track all your Concave asset s in one page.\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/ehdp3UaCWIoElOiDgU3Yv.png?height=1498&width=2880)\\n\\n[https://zapper.fi/zh/dashboard](https://zapper.fi/zh/dashboard)\\n\\n# 3.  Real-time data & chart\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/l-8u9bq-r0zCF_V0HhDRK.png?height=1387&width=2706)\\n\\n[https://www.dextools.io/app](https://www.dextools.io/app)\\n\\n# 4. an analytics tool for on-chain data\\n\\nDune. xyz is **an Ethereum data platform that offers access to the growing volume of blockchain data**. It provides the platform users, known as Dune Wizards, with the tools required to query, extract, and analyze large volumes of data from the blockchain.\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/D9Ub6ATP84_m9up6FlRxp.png?height=1498&width=2880)\\n\\n[https://dune.xyz/shadow/Olympus-(OHM)](https://dune.xyz/shadow/Olympus-(OHM))\\n\\n\",\"timestamp\":163842904